The bronze dart tip is a dart tip made with the Smithing skill. Players with at least 4 Smithing can smith 10 dart tips by using a bronze bar on an anvil with a hammer in their inventory. They can be fletched into bronze darts at level 10 Fletching when used with feathers, granting 18 Fletching experience per 10 darts made.

To smith darts, one must complete the Tourist Trap quest.

The '''bronze dart tip''' is a [[dart tip]] made with the [[Smithing]] skill. Players with at least 4 Smithing can smith 10 dart tips by using a [[bronze bar]] on an [[anvil]] with a [[hammer]] in their [[inventory]]. They can be fletched into [[bronze dart]]s at level 10 [[Fletching]] when used with [[feather]]s, granting 18 Fletching experience per 10 darts made.

To smith darts, one must complete the [[Tourist Trap]] quest.
